{
  "stem": "17135.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 112.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where it was such pressure, especially for the first one, the 1500, that they give special visas, special certificates.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after three weeks, they released us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were then distributed among the kibbutzim to get further training.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after us, every ship that was caught, they was sent to Cyprus if you remember.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were people two years in Cyprus after sitting in concentration camps, had to sit behind barbed wire in Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If I would have-- I-- I would have run away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I would have done it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "To sit-- you know, at least-- I fight with the British.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When I was in Atlit, I called them, you-- son-of-a-bitches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I provoked them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "One day they were running after me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Want to beat me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I couldn't stand-- Why were you angry with them?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And couldn't stand it. to be in a camp again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we married in '49.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "18 or I 19.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was very young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, two kids were--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two kids were born in Israel, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a kibbutz?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the-- they were born when we were in the kibbutz already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the first two years, I was elected the general manager of the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- we were stupid and we changed it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They only-- they made fun of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, not enough there was a Buchenwald in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to bring it to Israel?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We changed it to Kibbutz Netzer then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Between [NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH], but far from the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was actually between [NON-ENGLISH] and Ramla.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ramla was-- was the front.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were all in the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When the war broke out in [? '40, ?] everybody, the whole kibbutz were only women and children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I was first in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
